OOC: Sorry I haven't posted been way too busy.

::Aerotaur::
      "Trinity!!"  He runs after Windlord and spots the cave hearing 
Trinity's cry for help he goes in.  He sees her in the water but feels 
helpless as centaurs can't swim due to their shape.  In a fit of desperation 
he tries to transform again.  With the need to save her he returned to his 
semi-robot mode still retaining his wings.  He dove into the water and came 
up under her lifting her out of the waterand flying out into the sunlight.  
He bends over her and says "Trinity?  Can you hear me?"
